JdbcThinDatabaseMetadata should also be changed, currently it implements related methods as:
```
/** {@inheritDoc} */
@Override public int getDefaultTransactionIsolation() throws SQLException {
    return TRANSACTION_NONE;
}

/** {@inheritDoc} */
@Override public boolean supportsTransactions() throws SQLException {
    return false;
}

/** {@inheritDoc} */@Override public boolean supportsTransactionIsolationLevel(int level) throws SQLException {
    return false;
}
```
